学习八——正向传播、反向传播和计算图","uid":"4fbacb9593623ef87e625df2bc1cd56e","slug":"技术笔记/深度学习/深度学习八——正向传播、反向传播与计算图","date":"2021-11-18T12:02:19.000Z","updated":"2021-11-18T12:13:50.948Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/技术笔记/深度学习/深度学习八——正向传播、反向传播与计算图.json","cover":[],"text":" 正向传播、反向传播和计算图 到目前为止，我们已经用小批量随机梯度下降训练了我们的模型。然而，当我们实现该算法时，我们只考虑了通过模型 正向传播（forward propagation）所涉及的计算。在计算梯度时，我们只调用了深度学习框架提供的反向传播函数。 我们依赖一些基本的数...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.5k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"技术笔记","slug":"技术笔记","count":73,"path":"api/categories/技术笔记.json"},{"name":"深度学习","slug":"技术笔记/深度学习","count":11,"path":"api/categories/技术笔记/深度学习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"深度学习","slug":"深度学习","count":13,"path":"api/tags/深度学习.json"}],"author":{"name":"ZestJourney","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://zjpicture.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/20210822091020.jpg","link":"/","description":"吾好梦中读书~","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"QQ":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092319.jpg"},"WeiXin":{"icon":"/svg/weixin.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092515.png"},"Github":{"icon":"/svg/github.svg","link":"https://github.com/zestaken"}}}}},{"title":"深度学习七——模型选择、欠拟合和过拟合","uid":"2b624f6eb7de5f91607d66b1bfde997e","slug":"技术笔记/深度学习/深度学习七——模型选择、欠拟合和过拟合","date":"2021-11-18T08:03:19.000Z","updated":"2021-11-18T12:13:50.949Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/技术笔记/深度学习/深度学习七——模型选择、欠拟合和过拟合.json","cover":[],"text":" 模型选择、欠拟合和过拟合 泛化模式：作为机器学习科学家，我们的目标是发现模式（pattern）。但是，我们如何才能确定模型是真正发现了一种泛化的模式，而不是简单地记住了数据呢？例如，我们想要在患者的基因数据与痴呆状态之间寻找模式，其中标签是从集合{痴呆,轻度认知障碍,健康}\\{...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"22k","symbolsTime":"20 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"技术笔记","slug":"技术笔记","count":73,"path":"api/categories/技术笔记.json"},{"name":"深度学习","slug":"技术笔记/深度学习","count":11,"path":"api/categories/技术笔记/深度学习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"深度学习","slug":"深度学习","count":13,"path":"api/tags/深度学习.json"}],"author":{"name":"ZestJourney","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://zjpicture.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/20210822091020.jpg","link":"/","description":"吾好梦中读书~","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"QQ":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092319.jpg"},"WeiXin":{"icon":"/svg/weixin.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092515.png"},"Github":{"icon":"/svg/github.svg","link":"https://github.com/zestaken"}}}}},{"title":"深度学习六——多层感知机","uid":"2928f775bc3d3559bd67cd14c8aa549f","slug":"技术笔记/深度学习/深度学习六——多层感知机","date":"2021-11-18T07:13:19.000Z","updated":"2021-11-18T12:30:48.113Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/技术笔记/深度学习/深度学习六——多层感知机.json","cover":[],"text":" 多层感知机 最简单的深度网络称为多层感知机，它们由多层神经元组成，每一层都与下面一层（从中接收输入）和上面一层（反过来影响当前层的神经元）完全相连。 当我们训练大容量模型时，我们面临着过拟合的风险。因此，我们需要将了解包括过拟合、欠拟合和模型选择。为了解决这些问题，我们将使用权...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"20k","symbolsTime":"18 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"技术笔记","slug":"技术笔记","count":73,"path":"api/categories/技术笔记.json"},{"name":"深度学习","slug":"技术笔记/深度学习","count":11,"path":"api/categories/技术笔记/深度学习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"深度学习","slug":"深度学习","count":13,"path":"api/tags/深度学习.json"}],"author":{"name":"ZestJourney","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://zjpicture.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/20210822091020.jpg","link":"/","description":"吾好梦中读书~","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"QQ":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092319.jpg"},"WeiXin":{"icon":"/svg/weixin.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092515.png"},"Github":{"icon":"/svg/github.svg","link":"https://github.com/zestaken"